<div class="patternContent"><div class="patternTopic"> <h1><a name="Site_Fabric_Requirements"></a>  <strong><noop>Site Fabric Requirements</strong> </h1>
<p />
<div class="twikiToc"> <ul>
<li> <a href="?cover=print#Introduction_Site_Fabric_Require">Introduction--Site Fabric Requirements</a>
</li> <li> <a href="?cover=print#Desired_VDT_Installation_and_Fun">Desired VDT Installation and Functional Features</a>
</li> <li> <a href="?cover=print#Requested_clarifications_of_poli">Requested clarifications of policy</a>
